<br>
An /assist hotkey and really fast typing of /tar (short for /target)<br>
<br>
Assist hotkey's real simple, just label it &quot;Assist&quot; and have the first line be &quot;/assist&quot;.  Now target your mob (the big nasty thing wackin' on people) and assist, that's the person to heal.<br>
<br>
