<br>
By default it has no key binding. But if you go through options you will see something like &quot;toggle last target&quot; or something like that, and you can assign a key for it.<br>
<br>
I find this very handy if the MA isnt in my group, I target him, and then target the tank in my group.. and can then press 'q' (the key i bound the toggle thing to) to switch back and forwards between them.<br>
<br>
