<br>
After your cast, put a pause, then another cast.  That way if you fizzle, you get a second chance...   I find it is much easier than trying to frantically watching the spam fly by looking for the fizzle message and hitting the button again.  If the first cast goes, the second cast will give you some of error message, but, not interfere with the first one. <br>
<br>
So, for example, my c-heal is:<br>
/blah, blah , blah in whatever channel<br>
/cast 5<br>
/pause 1<br>
/cast 5<br>
